{"tid":1970832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際戰線煲大佢：廣州金拱門禁止黑人進入","createTime":"2020-04-13T12:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T15:34:54.000Z","uid":263344,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3ec34d56c0e634ca4f9e7ba140f61c8d51802aeb","tid":1970832,"uid":263344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T12:36:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.winandmac.com/2020/04/africans-are-not-allowed-to-enter-mcdonalds/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2F2020%2F04%2Fafricans-are-not-allowed-to-enter-mcdonalds%2F&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWRjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=e1389a94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.winandmac.com/2020/04/africans-are-not-allowed-to-enter-mcdonalds/</a><br />\n<br />\n廣州早前發生黑人被趕到街頭的情況，當局聲稱是為了防疫，但事實上就算這些黑人沒有感染武漢肺炎，以及完成家居檢疫，也被趕出街。英文網站shanghaiist報道，這些黑人就算要去麥當勞吃東西，也被人拒於門外，十足十當年美國黑人被種族歧視的情況。"},{"pid":"b4175bc00d7f5ab4f154d6eb7a35a118ad6f7e3e","tid":1970832,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T12:38:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"75ce2dff951ccb4a09aaccd584e04b23c665d2fa","tid":1970832,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T12:38:26.000Z","msg":"中資<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e27b158613188a7a2c92c44064a5d0e40840b8","tid":1970832,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T12:38:53.000Z","msg":"ho ball, 賤鬥賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"594339223744fe7943c2653f52aff97de434ed9f","tid":1970832,"uid":31017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T12:40:54.000Z","msg":"共匪引入黑人蘇州屎<br />\n唔使執呀"},{"pid":"0f600e355580b0be9f1631ee8b7f74fafed3c708","tid":1970832,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T12:47:35.000Z","msg":"racist <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7494